response.overview: In the middle of a hard decision and grief, a young woman comes back to her first habitat. She feels and recognizes her deep connection to many women in that symbolic place. Hold by all of them she continues walking to transform her fear and navigate new horizons.
response.tagline: In the middle of a hard decision and grief, a young woman comes back to her first habitat to transform her fear and navigate new horizons.
response.title: Habitat
